{
  "stem": "23428.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] So it was refusal as well as-- as-- as anger.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Very much so.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "As I said, we had to move out of our luxurious dwellings and to a much more modest place that my mother could administer by herself.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And of course, I was excluded from going to-- to go to high school.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was just through the helpfulness of the Jesuits that-- that they allowed me to-- to pass-- to enter their school, which was being abolished into second class of high school into the first, which is why I always went to the same class with my brother.",
      "word_count": 47
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, none whatsoever.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "None whatsoever.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The regime was totally uninterested in people's religion.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Our status was defined by the Nuremberg laws, nothing else.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, the-- the legislation that didn't allows us to have servants.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, it was enforced [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] like all laws are enforced.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, once you say that no-- no domestic can work in a Jewish household, domestics had to leave.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I don't think there was a problem of enforcement.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, well, this is even much more so the case in Germany than it's in this country.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know, if there's a law promulgated, it is instantly obeyed by everybody.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That's what people are educated to do.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He had-- he already was gone since 1936.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I mean, he was not-- his life-- I understand he was in fear of imprisonment in 1936.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I don't know who forewarned him, but I suspect the same people we will be talking about later, who led to his employment by the-- by the German army in later course.",
      "word_count": 33
    }
  ],
